\t> 关联 PRD：[prd/v1-mvp.md](./v1-mvp.md)\n     7\t\n     8\t## 1. 背景与目标\n
    9\t\n    10\t### 背景\n    11\tSocial World 的 IM 系统是匹配成功后的核心社交
场景。用户在双向匹配后可以开启一对一实时聊天，通过文字和图片加深了解。IM 体验的
实时性和稳定性直接影响用户留存。\n    12\t\n    13\t### 目标\n    14\t1. 支持匹
配成功的用户进入会话并发送文本/图片消息。\n    15\t2. 支持消息的实时收发（在线用
户 < 1 秒到达）。\n    16\t3. 支持消息已读回执和未读数实时同步。\n    17\t4. 支
持离线用户通过推送提醒新消息。\n    18\t5. 支持历史消息分页拉取。\n    19\t6. 保
证消息顺序性和幂等性（防止重复发送）。\n    20\t\n    21\t---\n    22\t\n    23\
t## 2. 用户故事与验收标准\n    24\t\n    25\t### US-IM-1：进入会话并发送第一条消
息\n    26\t\n    27\t**作为** 匹配成功的用户，  \n    28\t**我希望** 打开会话后
看到系统提示并能发送消息，  \n    29\t**以便** 与对方开始聊天。\n    30\t\n    3
1\t#### 验收标准\n    32\t> 以上验收标准的完整 Gherkin 用例详见 `tests/bdd/im.fe
ature`。\n    33\t\n    34\t```gherkin\n    35\tFeature: Start Chatting After Ma
tch\n    36\t  Scenario: Matched users see system welcome message\n    37\t    G
iven Alice and Bob have matched successfully\n    38\t    When Alice opens the c
onversation with Bob\n    39\t    Then Alice should see the system message "你们
已匹配成功，开始聊天吧"\n    40\t    And the conversation_id should be the one c
reated at match time\n    41\t\n    42\t  Scenario: User sends a text message\n 
  43\t    Given Alice is in the conversation with Bob\n    44\t    When Alice ty
pes "你好" and sends\n    45\t    Then Bob should receive the message within 1 s
econd if online\n    46\t    And the message should be persisted in the messages
table\n    47\t    And the message status should progress from "sending" to "sen
t" to "delivered"\n    48\t```\n    49\t\n    50\t#### 技术要求\n    51\t- 打开
会话时，若数据库中无系统消息记录，后端自动插入一条 `type = \'system\'` 的消息作
为欢迎语。\n    52\t- 文本消息限制 500 字符，超出则前端禁止发送或后端拒绝（`code
=1000`）。\n    53\t- 消息表字段：`id`, `conversation_id`, `sender_id`, `type`（
`text`/`image`/`system`）, `content`, `client_message_id`, `sequence_id`, `statu
s`, `created_at`。\n    54\t\n    55\t---\n    56\t\n    57\t### US-IM-2：实时消
息收发\n    58\t\n    59\t**作为** 在线用户，  \n    60\t**我希望** 消息实时送达
，  \n    61\t**以便** 获得流畅的聊天体验。\n    62\t\n    63\t#### 验收标准\n  
 64\t> 以上验收标准的完整 Gherkin 用例详见 `tests/bdd/im.feature`。\n    65\t\n 
  66\t```gherkin\n    67\tFeature: Real-Time Message Delivery\n    68\t  Scenari
o: Online user receives message instantly\n    69\t    Given Alice and Bob are b
oth online and connected via Socket.io\n    70\t    When Alice sends "在吗？"\n 
  71\t    Then Bob should receive the message within 1 second\n    72\t    And B
ob\'s unread count for this conversation should increase by 1\n    73\t    And t
he message status should become "delivered" on Alice\'s side\n    74\t\n    75\t
 Scenario: Offline user receives push notification\n    76\t    Given Bob is off
line and Alice is online\n    77\t    When Alice sends "晚上一起吃饭？"\n    78\
t    Then the message should be persisted\n    79\t    And Bob\'s unread count s
hould increase by 1 in Redis\n    80\t    And a push notification should be trig
gered for Bob\n    81\t```\n    82\t\n    83\t#### 技术要求\n    84\t- Socket.io
Gateway：`apps/api/src/modules/im/im.gateway.ts`。\n    85\t- 事件约定：\n    86
\t  - Client → Server：`message:send`（`conversation_id`, `content`, `type`, `cl
ient_message_id`）\n    87\t  - Server → Client：`message:receive`（完整消息体，
广播给接收方）\n    88\t  - Server → Client：`message:ack`（`client_message_id`,
`sequence_id`，确认发送方消息已入库）\n    89\t- 在线判定：用户连接 Socket.io 时
加入以 `user_id` 命名的 Room；断开时离开 Room。\n    90\t- 未读数：Redis `unread
_count:{user_id}:{conversation_id}`，收到消息时 `INCR`。\n    91\t- 离线推送：接
收方不在线时，调用 Push Service 发送通知（极光/Firebase 骨架）。\n    92\t\n    
93\t---\n    94\t\n    95\t### US-IM-3：已读回执\n    96\t\n    97\t**作为** 发
送方，  \n    98\t**我希望** 看到对方是否已读我的消息，  \n    99\t**以便** 了解
对方的回应意愿。\n   100\t\n   101\t#### 验收标准\n   102\t> 以上验收标准的完整 
Gherkin 用例详见 `tests/bdd/im.feature`。\n   103\t\n   104\t```gherkin\n   105\
tFeature: Read Receipts\n   106\t  Scenario: Receiver opens conversation and mar
ks messages as read\n   107\t    Given Bob has received 3 unread messages from A
lice\n   108\t    When Bob opens the conversation\n   109\t    Then all unread m
essages from Alice should be marked as "read"\n   110\t    And Alice should see 
the message status change to "已读" for the last message\n   111\t    And Bob\'s
unread count for this conversation should be reset to 0\n   112\t\n   113\t  Sce
nario: Sender sees read status update in real time\n   114\t    Given Alice sent
a message to Bob\n   115\t    And Bob has received it\n   116\t    When Bob open
s the conversation\n   117\t    Then Alice should receive a "message:read_receip
t" event via Socket.io\n   118\t    And the event should contain the last_read_m
essage_id\n   119\t```\n   120\t\n   121\t#### 技术要求\n   122\t- Client → Serv
er：`message:read`（`conversation_id`, `last_message_id`）\n   123\t- Server 行
为：\n   124\t  1. 更新 `conversation_participants.last_read_message_id`（当前用
户在该会话中的最后已读消息）。\n   125\t  2. Redis `unread_count:{user_id}:{conv
ersation_id}` 重置为 0。\n   126\t  3. 向对方广播 `message:read_receipt`（`conve
rsation_id`, `last_read_message_id`）。\n   127\t- Mobile 侧根据 `last_read_mess
age_id` 和消息 `sequence_id` 决定哪些消息显示「已读」状态。\n   128\t\n   129\t-
--\n   130\t\n   131\t### US-IM-4：会话列表与未读数\n   132\t\n   133\t**作为** 
用户，  \n   134\t**我希望** 看到所有会话列表和未读消息数，  \n   135\t**以便** 
快速定位需要回复的聊天。\n   136\t\n   137\t#### 验收标准\n   138\t> 以上验收标
准的完整 Gherkin 用例详见 `tests/bdd/im.feature`。\n   139\t\n   140\t```gherkin
\n   141\tFeature: Conversation List\n   142\t  Scenario: User sees conversation
list with unread counts\n   143\t    Given Alice has conversations with Bob (3 u
nread) and Charlie (0 unread)\n   144\t    When Alice opens the conversation lis
t\n   145\t    Then she should see 2 conversations ordered by last_message_time 
descending\n   146\t    And the conversation with Bob should display unread coun
t 3\n   147\t    And the conversation with Charlie should display unread count 0
\n   148\t\n   149\t  Scenario: New message updates conversation list in real ti
me\n   150\t    Given Alice is viewing the conversation list\n   151\t    When B
ob sends a new message to Alice\n   152\t    Then Alice\'s conversation list sho
uld update within 1 second\n   153\t    And Bob\'s conversation should move to t
he top\n   154\t    And the unread count should increase by 1\n   155\t```\n   1
56\t\n   157\t#### 技术要求\n   158\t- 接口：`GET /conversations?limit=20&cursor
=`（游标分页）。\n   159\t- 返回体包含：\n   160\t  - `conversation_id`\n   161\
t  - `matched_user`（`user_id`, `nickname`, `avatar_url`）\n   162\t  - `last_me
ssage`（`content`, `type`, `created_at`）\n   163\t  - `unread_count`\n   164\t-
未读数来源：Redis `unread_count:{user_id}:{conversation_id}`。\n   165\t- 实时更
新：Socket.io 广播 `conversation:updated` 事件给会话双方，触发 Mobile 刷新列表。
\n   166\t\n   167\t---\n   168\t\n   169\t### US-IM-5：历史消息拉取\n   170\t\n
  171\t**作为** 用户，  \n   172\t**我希望** 进入聊天页时能看到历史消息，  \n   
173\t**以便** 回顾之前的聊天内容。\n   174\t\n   175\t#### 验收标准\n   176\t> 
以上验收标准的完整 Gherkin 用例详见 `tests/bdd/im.feature`。\n   177\t\n   178\t
```gherkin\n   179\tFeature: Message History\n   180\t  Scenario: User loads his
torical messages\n   181\t    Given Alice and Bob have exchanged 50 messages\n  
182\t    When Alice opens the conversation\n   183\t    Then the app should load
the most recent 20 messages\n   184\t    And older messages should be loaded whe
n Alice scrolls up\n   185\t\n   186\t  Scenario: Message order is preserved\n  
187\t    Given Alice sent messages A, B, C in sequence\n   188\t    When Bob ope
ns the conversation\n   189\t    Then Bob should see A, B, C in the exact same o
rder\n   190\t```\n   191\t\n   192\t#### 技术要求\n   193\t- 接口：`GET /messag
es?conversation_id=xxx&cursor=&limit=20`（游标分页，Cursor 为 `sequence_id`）。\
n   194\t- 消息排序：按 `sequence_id ASC`（数据库自增 `bigserial`）。\n   195\t-
客户端本地缓存：Mobile 使用本地数据库（如 `sqflite`）缓存最近 N 条消息，减少重复
拉取。\n   196\t\n   197\t---\n   198\t\n   199\t### US-IM-6：消息幂等性与顺序保
证\n   200\t\n   201\t**作为** 用户，  \n   202\t**我希望** 消息不会重复发送，  
\n   203\t**以便** 聊天记录保持整洁。\n   204\t\n   205\t#### 验收标准\n   206\t
> 以上验收标准的完整 Gherkin 用例详见 `tests/bdd/im.feature`。\n   207\t\n   208
\t```gherkin\n   209\tFeature: Message Idempotency and Ordering\n   210\t  Scena
rio: Duplicate message is deduplicated\n   211\t    Given Alice sends a message 
with client_message_id "msg-001"\n   212\t    When the network fluctuates and Al
ice sends the same message again with "msg-001"\n   213\t    Then the server sho
uld store only one message record\n   214\t    And both requests should return t
he same sequence_id\n   215\t\n   216\t  Scenario: Messages are ordered by seque
nce_id\n   217\t    Given Alice sends messages "Hi", "How are you?", "Good night
" in rapid succession\n   218\t    Then each message should be assigned an incre
menting sequence_id\n   219\t    And Bob should receive them in the exact same o
rder\n   220\t```\n   221\t\n   222\t#### 技术要求\n   223\t- 客户端生成 `client
_message_id`（UUID v4 或雪花算法）。\n   224\t- 服务端 `messages` 表建立唯一索引
`(conversation_id, client_message_id)`。\n   225\t- 重复发送时捕获唯一索引冲突，
返回已存在的消息记录和 `sequence_id`。\n   226\t- `sequence_id` 使用数据库自增 `
bigserial`，作为消息排序的唯一依据。\n   227\t\n   228\t---\n   229\t\n   230\t#
# 3. 非功能需求\n   231\t\n   232\t### 性能\n   233\t- 在线消息到达时间 < 1 秒（
P95）。\n   234\t- 会话列表加载时间 < 500ms。\n   235\t- 历史消息分页加载时间 < 
300ms。\n   236\t- 单会话消息数达到 10 万时，分页查询仍 < 500ms（依赖索引优化）
。\n   237\t\n   238\t### 安全\n   239\t- 只有会话成员才能发送和读取消息（Socket
.io Gateway 校验 `conversation_participants` 表）。\n   240\t- 非成员尝试发送消
息时，Gateway 返回错误并可选断开连接。\n   241\t- 消息内容预留敏感词过滤接口（MV
P 阶段可先用简单关键词列表拦截）。\n   242\t\n   243\t### 兼容性\n   244\t- Sock
et.io 连接支持自动重连（Mobile 侧配置 5 次重连，退避策略）。\n   245\t- 重连后客
户端拉取 `last_ack_sequence_id` 之后的所有消息，补发离线期间的消息。\n   246\t\n
